}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device is apparently used in the BDP-S560 Blu-ray player.
"3753-60000104G" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
This device is shown with two [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=946 '''SiGe''' ('''Skyworks''') 2548A / SE2548A dual band a/b/g/n front end modules].
A MAC label on the device in the FCC photos has a MAC with a 00:01:36 ('''CyberTAN''') OUI.
